Package: stemr
Type: Package
Title: Fit Stochastic Epidemic Models via Bayesian Data Augmentation
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: as.person(c(
    "Jon Fintzi <fintzij@uw.edu> [aut, cre]",
    "Jon Wakefield <jonno@uw.edu> [aut]",
    "Vladimir Minin <vminin@uw.edu> [aut]"
  ))
URL: https://github.com/fintzij/stemr
BugReports: https://github.com/fintzij/stemr/issues
Description: Fit stochastic epidemic models using Bayesian data augmentation.
    Implements an agent-based data-driven data augmentation algorithm for
    efficient subject-level path proposals based on noisy aggregate counts at
    discrete observation times.
License: GPL-3
